The following units are also included in this Department:
The Maryland Membership Unit of the Interstate Commission of the Potomac River Basin;
The Maryland Membership Unit of the Susquehanna River Basin Commission;
The Maryland Membership Unit of the Atlantic States Marine Fisheries Commission;
The Maryland Membership Unit of the Potomac River Fisheries Commission;
The Maryland Membership Unit of the Interstate Oil and Gas Compact Commission; and
The Maryland Membership Unit of the Interstate Mining Commission.
